    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the end<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> keeping the stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> intact</p><p>Without cutting through the stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>, carefully slice the<strong> trimmed courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into thin strips, lengthways (at approx. 5mm intervals)</p><p>Then peel the lengths of the<strong> sliced courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>until you have a pile of 'courgetti'</p><p>Tip: Have a spiraliser? Use this instead!</p>",
